## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="5adc3-151">下面的示例使用 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.Choices> 和 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.GrammarBuilder> 对象创建语音识别语法。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="5adc3-151">The following example creates a speech recognition grammar using <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.Choices> and <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.GrammarBuilder> objects.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="5adc3-152"><xref:System.Speech.Recognition.Grammar.%23ctor%2A> 构造函数从 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.GrammarBuilder> 对象创建 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.Grammar> 对象。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="5adc3-152">The <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.Grammar.%23ctor%2A> constructor creates a <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.Grammar> object from the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.GrammarBuilder> object.</span></span>  
  
```csharp
// Create a grammar using a GrammarBuilder and return the new grammar.   
private static Grammar CreateGrammarBuilderGrammar()  
{  
  GrammarBuilder builder = new GrammarBuilder();  
  
  Choices cityChoice = new Choices (new string[]   
  {"Seattle", "New York", "Miami", "Los Angeles"});  
  
  builder.Append("I would like to fly from");  
  builder.Append(cityChoice);  
  builder.Append("to");  
  builder.Append(cityChoice);  
  
  Grammar citiesGrammar = new Grammar(builder);  
  citiesGrammar.Name = "GrammarBuilder Cities Grammar";  
  
  return citiesGrammar;  
}  
```

  
  
